title: Aiden Discography
description:
This torrent contains an up to date archive of every Aiden album, including Wil's solo album under his alias 'William Control', and a few extras as well. Everything included is listed below:


Studio Albums:
Knives(2009)
Hate Culture(2008 | William Control)
Conviction(2007)
Nightmare Anatomy(2005)
Our Gangs Dark Oath(2004)

EPs:
Rain In Hell

Singles:
"Cry Little Sister" - from The Lost Boys Soundtrack

Covers:
"Drain You" - A Nirvana Cover

Seed and enjoy. =)
